{"tid":2460997,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：北京多名受訪市民稱會抵制H&M產品","createTime":"2021-03-25T07:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T07:38:51.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8be58480d7dea70d67e52b940e159c04d1484204","tid":2460997,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"內地多個官方媒體批評瑞典服裝品牌H&amp;M有關沒有購買新疆棉花產品的聲明。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，多名受訪的市民均表明，會抵制H&amp;M的產品。有市民認為，<strong>想賺中國人的錢，就要尊重中國人</strong>。對於新彊問題，他指外國需要調查實際情況才發言。<br />\n<br />\n另一名市民表示，<strong>新彊是棉花最好的出產地</strong>，認為比H&amp;M等外來快銷品牌的衣服材質為高。她認為，<strong>中國人要自強，不在意外來品牌是否扺制中國好的原材料</strong>，中國亦有足夠人口，有龐大消費市場支持新彊棉。<br />\n<br />\n至於在北京朝陽區的H&amp;M分店，仍有市民內進購物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582523-20210325.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582523-20210325.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxjWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=c0943c91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582523-20210325.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5a1b9a8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582523-20210325.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"673fcf3818ddf8cb8f871b5f00bf792f7b6279ff","tid":2460997,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"至於在北京朝陽區的H&amp;M分店，仍有市民內進購物。<br />\n<br />\n買開嗰啲真係wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547e6a0ad283688b7e1390bc7c2a1ef1d6ce3584","tid":2460997,"uid":71086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:34:06.000Z","msg":"抵制日貨<br />\n結果呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2915b4a21c9342ff532a5779298a26e451a3f3a","tid":2460997,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc